📊 Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) Project

📌 Project Overview:

This project focuses on performing Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on a cleaned dataset using Microsoft Excel. The main goal was to understand data patterns, detect trends, and extract meaningful insights to support decision making.
🎯 Objectives:

•Understand dataset structure and variables

•Identify patterns and trends in data

•Detect outliers and anomalies

•Perform basic statistical analysis

•Summarize key insights from data

•Prepare data for further visualization or modeling

🔍 Steps Performed:

•Imported cleaned dataset into Excel

•Checked data structure and columns

•Performed descriptive statistics (mean, median, mode)

•Analyzed distributions of key variables

•Identified missing values or inconsistencies 

•Detected outliers in numerical data

•Created summary tables for insights

•Interpreted results for business understanding

📁 Files Included:

•Cleaned Dataset

•EDA Analysis File (Excel)

•Summary Insights 

🛠 Tools Used:

•Microsoft Excel

📌 Key Insights:

•Data shows clear patterns in key variables

•Some outliers were detected and analyzed

•Overall dataset is suitable for further analysis

